<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176633>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7 A – O. Chilicola nanula Packer, n. sp. Head of male: A. lateral view, B. frontal view. Head of female: C. lateral view, D. frontal view. E. maxillary palpus of female. Male: F. pronotum. G. hind leg. H. S 7. I. S 8. J. genital capsule. Dorsal views are at the left. K – O. Sting apparatus of female: K. hemitergite 7, L. hemitergite 8, M. First and second valvifer with gonostylus, N. sting shaft. O. furcula. Stippling in A and B indicates pale colouration, in J and M it indicates membranous areas." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/176633/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

